{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "萧秋水在嵩山少林寺父母墓碑前祭拜，左丘超然、罗海牛、杀仔三人前来寻他。杀仔告知广东五虎与各地年轻武人组建了\"神州结义\"组织，欲在湖南召开长江大会推选盟主，请萧秋水前往。萧秋水询问左丘超然梁大哥等人的下落时，左丘超然突然出手制住他四处要穴，暴露其朱大天王义子身份。杀仔愤怒上前质问，罗海牛趁机拔出杀仔的石锤与秧钉将其杀害。萧秋水冷冷与罗海牛对峙，以言语揭露其不仁不义。左丘超然暗中以功力反震自身关节，萧秋水趁机以长歌剑刺杀罗海牛。萧秋水审问左丘超然，得知朱大天王暗中控制义子、觊觎天下英雄令的阴谋，以及梁大哥等人被掌握的情况。此时天山剑派杀手娄小叶突现，飞剑射伤左丘超然双眼，萧秋水为减轻左丘痛苦将其杀死。娄小叶自报身份，乃朱大天王义子头领，自创柳叶剑法，杀人无数。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_zai",
      "speaker_name": "杀仔",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "萧大哥，我们两厂八虎，已经约好了帮手，总联络处就设在湖南，专门对付权力帮、朱大天王等狗贼的。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很好，很好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_zai",
      "speaker_name": "杀仔",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我们就暂且把那组织称作'神州结义'，乃沿用萧大哥所创的名字……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_sha_zai",
      "text": "神州结义'？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_zai",
      "speaker_name": "杀仔",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "对！就是'神州结义'！我们这就去会合！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_sha_zai",
      "text": "我？要我去……？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_zai",
      "speaker_name": "杀仔",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "是疯女、阿水姐她们要我和阿牛来接你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "正是。他们现下就要开'长江大会'，挑选盟主，萧大哥快去一趟。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_zai",
      "speaker_name": "杀仔",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "这些结集的人士，多是来自各地年轻武人，也有各派精英高手……他们都有胆识，不畏强仅，但近日来敢于抗暴者，自然以萧大哥为最，你去，他们一定选你……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "萧大哥是众望所归。萧大哥是人中豪杰，我等特来请您过去一趟，并愿为您效忠，至死不渝，如若违约，天打雷劈，横尸神州……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_zai",
      "speaker_name": "杀仔",
      "listener": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "text": "阿牛你又何必出口那么重呢。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_sha_zai",
      "text": "因为我问心无愧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "你不是与梁大哥等一道吗？他们呢？到哪里去了！我一直在找，找上了金顶……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "左丘，你……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "为什么……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我不是权力帮的人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "你究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我是朱大天王义子，我要拿的是'天下英雄令'。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_zai",
      "speaker_name": "杀仔",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "你妈的王八兔崽儿子，你居然是朱大天上的伙计混出来的卧底？！你他妈的孬种孬到咱'神州结义'来了？！你有没带眼识人呀你？！我宝安阿杀只要在，就捶扁你的猪脑袋……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_zai",
      "speaker_name": "杀仔",
      "listener": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "text": "你们……你……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_zai",
      "speaker_name": "杀仔",
      "listener": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "text": "我……我做鬼都不……放过……你……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你又猜我是谁？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "text": "你知道我最喜欢什么人？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我怎知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "text": "我最喜欢的人，是仁、义、忠、信之士。最恨的人，是不忠；弃义、背信、无仁之徒，但这些都不是你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "原来你不恨我。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "text": "我当然不恨你。因为你根本不是人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "text": "杀害自己兄弟的人，能算作人吗？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "左丘，杀了他！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "杀了他才搜'天下英雄令'！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "你不忍做，我做！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "text": "这是你出卖兄弟，所得的报应。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "text": "我杀了你来祭我的剑。它第一次就饮你这种非人的血。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "他又为什么要这样做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "他跟我一样，都认朱大天王作干爹。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "他要那未多干儿子来干嘛？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "因为他没有老婆。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "你们愿意这样做？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "罗海牛自大，认为他长袖善舞，从善如流，地位应在其他几头小老虎之上，所以不惜出卖，第一个就先要格倒你，再由朱大天王另立首领，来取代你的地位，夺得领导'神州结义'的宗主权。所以他要暗算你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "但是你呢？你又是为啥呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我的师父是项释儒……养父是鹰爪下雷锋……父亲是左丘道亭……我不忍他们死！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "难道……令尊等亦在朱大天王的威胁之下？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "梁大哥、老铁，小邱等……是不是在你们掌握之中？！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "他们在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lou_xiao_ye",
      "speaker_name": "娄小叶",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我叫娄小叶，我是一个很有名的杀手，你大概听说过吧？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    }
  ],
